title: One Piece - Return to Innocence (Doujinshi)
description:
A One Piece pixiv doujinshi.

Luffy accidentally walks in on Robin taking a bath. While waiting for her to finish, the two have a heart-to-heart-talk. Robin begins to realize where her place where she belongs is.
